Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.54,0:00:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行 快停工
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.17,0:00:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 正準備動工呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.56,0:00:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.25,0:00:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說團藏大人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.51,0:00:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第六代火影沒了 取消了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.26,0:00:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明認認真真準備了 連夢裡都是團藏大人的臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.56,0:00:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白費力氣了 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.84,0:00:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下來誰當火影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.85,0:00:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這名忍者原本是大蛇丸的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.42,0:00:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在成為佐助的夥伴之後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.18,0:00:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾以曉的身份行動過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.17,0:00:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說知曉很多內幕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.65,0:01:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好對待我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且目睹了佐助同團藏的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.33,0:01:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到他們二人對決了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡就開始審問了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.16,0:01:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 這傢伙就交由我們情報部看管
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.38,0:01:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會問出她知道的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶走她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.18,0:01:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.79,0:01:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.93,0:01:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.06,0:01:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我放手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.62,0:01:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口乾死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我拿些飲料來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 綱手大人情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.47,0:01:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依舊昏迷不醒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.97,0:01:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也該去向上級匯報了 這就告辭…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西 木葉村現在雜亂無章
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.23,0:02:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得盡早有人站出來穩定大局啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助…竟然做出這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 佐助的事希望你們交給我處理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要一個人對付佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明知道我們不會同意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如天天所說 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能任由你耍性子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問為什麼的話 這可是事關村子的大事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才不是耍性子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼回來之後會詳細說明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還在想你會說些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也下了解決佐助的決心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會嘴上說一個人去處理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際暗地包庇佐助吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我沒有包庇佐助的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鳥 螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大鬧五影會談
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又跟團藏對決 即使是佐助也很虛弱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.81,0:05:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有一口氣收拾他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑也在 不是那麼容易就能辦到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.43,0:05:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不應該眼睜睜看著他們逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 你可是很強的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是打倒了佩因的英雄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對付佐助時也該像那時一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.31,0:05:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅憑那樣無法打倒現在的佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點我很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的內心…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.25,0:05:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之 誰也不能跟現在的佐助交手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠與之交手的只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.47,0:06:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣根本就沒說清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我解釋清楚點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機成熟自然會說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又想打馬虎眼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀懂我心裡的真正想法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你也預見到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.13,0:06:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你我交戰的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.14,0:06:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個都會死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底隱瞞了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,0:06:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼回事了 拜託各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.23,0:06:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連團藏也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 優秀的傢伙都競相離去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來趕緊召開決定火影人選的會議
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.77,0:07:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於忍者聯軍的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火影不在也無法進展啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去也不是辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們推薦你為火影
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同盟砂影也推薦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經做好覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺直白的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好 雖然火影並不適合我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 也好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就去向大名們申請召開會議
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被傳喚之前 在村子裡做好準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有什麼需要做準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事先向你這位繼任火影說明一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團藏確實是個野心家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他都是全心全意為了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外有日斬 內有團藏的年代可是木葉的黃金時期啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這該怎麼解讀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想獨自承擔一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身邊有人輔佐是最理想的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時的夥伴只剩下我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者的命運真是難以琢磨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 我似乎就要當火影了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.93,0:09:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來平安無事地回來了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 那就進行久違的比賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 問為什麼 現在還問什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我和你是永遠的對手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止超越數百次的對戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日繼續一戰而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.90,0:09:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准用寫輪眼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭…剪刀…布
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NO 石頭剪刀布絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝負在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那上面設置了終點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.08,0:09:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看誰先到 如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是幹這事的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:10:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為這個時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才想同你進行熱血之戰 卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠接受吧 我永遠的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊 只有趁現在了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起點還特意設在村子入口嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場比賽我可打算好好享受一番呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候發令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候弄出那東西來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽開始前從廢墟中翻出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.92,0:11:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想鳴人的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄吧 想了也是白想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人要是不說的話 就一無所知了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.05,0:12:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重建中的村子的路況
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不能像以往一樣事先預測了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話大家都不會認可的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.45,0:12:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:13:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻認同了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是覺得鳴人有什麼計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以決定相信你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.38,0:13:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西老師和凱老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩人 不會又來那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.89,0:13:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人的勝負對決 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定又是凱老師挑起的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 在這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 正因為這種時候才挑起的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我的對手卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝負現在才開始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱老師在對決的時候 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要一同戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李 哪個勝了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是卡卡西老師勝了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不錯的對決呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.15,0:14:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是比賽取勝了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你就任火影
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為火影后就不能隨意同我對決了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在那之前 我想跟你進行最後的對決
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才不會是最後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你我是永遠的對手這點永不變
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱 有你在我也踏實很多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡…卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.79,0:15:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人來保護村子也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是旗木卡卡西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一任火影
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我量一下你的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想確定一下臉型
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影巖啊 影巖 火影的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在跟我走一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要成為火影好像也很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我永遠的對手捷足先登了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 接下來是凱老師超越他的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西當上了火影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目標定在他前面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走在火影之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.62,0:16:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個遙遠的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.69,0:16:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧 凱老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.86,0:16:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 火影的前面是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,髮型這樣行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:16:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護額斜掛就好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.53,0:17:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦開始雕刻 就不能隨意更改了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.74,0:17:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有遺漏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來準備注模
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是石膏嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將這個在你臉上薄薄地塗上一層
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.59,0:17:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定型測量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要快點搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個能否取下來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面罩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做石像把臉給遮住怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 快來人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜音 難不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.67,0:18:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯答應真是救急了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿角願意當火影的話我就得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.41,0:18:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別亂說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就算把瑣事交給兒子然後隱居也毫不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.54,0:18:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是說這個的時候呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團藏居然會在跟曉的戰鬥中陣亡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.30,0:18:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 不得不確認新的火影
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一致推薦旗木卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.69,0:18:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旗木卡卡西 進來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.97,0:18:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 那麼旗木卡卡西 你就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.08,0:18:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大名大人 有何不妥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒什麼 要任命他為第幾代火影呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第幾代嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.43,0:19:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團藏雖是第六代…但正式就任前就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.12,0:19:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任命卡卡西為第六代還是第七代呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算正式就任前陣亡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.49,0:19:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團藏也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缺一個 還是第六代
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還是第七代
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是第六代實際上… 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.77,0:19:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旗木卡卡西 任命你為…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事 現在可是重要的會議之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.52,0:19:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我前來報告緊急事件
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 有何突變
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜音 好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.70,0:20:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳令給其他村子 告知木葉的火影綱手健在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也把這件事傳達給別國的大名們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村裡的人也要盡快通知
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.94,0:20:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.24,0:20:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得到這裡了 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吃回轉壽司吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.12,0:20:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來比賽能吃多少盤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行 停手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人好像恢復火影職位了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 又白費力氣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.00,0:22:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你來沒別的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.24,0:22:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰來著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好歹長點記性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.87,0:22:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.24,0:22:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了關於你的預言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.19,0:22:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.31,0:22:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.46,0:22:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛤蟆仙人的預言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.93,0:23:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下水落石出了
